commit.message: Accept a basic message and return to user
Use UUID as picture name and send that as a response to Lex
Exclude as many libraries as possible w/o causing it to break
Explicitly exclude unused dependencies from amazonica
Implement code that uploads an MMS message to S3
Remove unused dev dependencies and plugins
Add sample request that can be used for ad-hoc testing
Hooking up all the logic in the handler
Add sanitize function to help convert raw twilio requests
Only send message when there is one, returns nil if nothing happened
Re-create sample input stream on every call as it gets closed
Add dummy methods that quickly test functionality ad-hoc
Remove the essthree plugin and configuration
Eliminate :refer and use :as to provide better dependency context
